## Navigation Order

Tabs appear in this order (conceptual dependency):
1. cases - Framework for understanding Greek
2. pronouns - Cases in action (most frequent words)
3. articles - Same patterns applied to nouns
4. adjectives - Agreement following article patterns
5. prepositions - Combines with articles/pronouns
6. verbs - Separate system (conjugation)
7. patterns - Special constructions
